{"tid":684524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被槍殺反普京記者突現身記招　詐死令俄羅斯特工曝光","createTime":"2018-05-30T15:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T00:19:42.000Z","uid":5195,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa293ce94b37f54f4f9213f738a58a323acb647","tid":684524,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:15:56.000Z","msg":"一度傳出死訊的俄羅斯籍記者巴布琴科，在烏克蘭基輔一個電視播出的記者會現身。烏克蘭保安部門主管在記者會上說，巴布琴科被殺的事是一場戲，目的是令俄羅斯特工曝光。<br />\n<br />\n現年41歲的巴布琴科，曾經是俄羅斯知名戰地記者。他經常批評俄羅斯總統普京及俄軍的行動，去年移居基輔。傳媒早前廣泛報道，巴布琴科回家時遭槍手伏擊，背部連中幾槍，送院期間不治。<br />\n<br />\n在記者會上，巴布琴科向似乎不知情的妻子道歉。"},{"pid":"f78bc78767c8eb77ddb1a645009691f5b00ebe81","tid":684524,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:20:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34debe69110f94fcca6d30b9a1c48324246369ec","tid":684524,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66841816ae368325bee7d52e30f4d1a9611de508","tid":684524,"uid":98659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"mission impossible<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f44db09bdcc547d6f86c7e89a6305b3a76d652","tid":684524,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66841816ae368325bee7d52e30f4d1a9611de508","tid":684524,"uid":98659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"mission impossible<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:48:34.000Z","msg":"最尾都要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fb68c94a41ddcada10e491bb2ff10963978451","tid":684524,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"唔死先係新聞吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b8494f